@were For an executor `exe`, you can use `arg_dict` and `grad_dict`. For example

``` python
for k, v in exe.arg_dict.items():
   print(k, v.asnumpy())
for k, v in exe.grad_dict.items():
   print(k, v.asnumpy())
```
